    <text xml:id="Site_WFY_Section_Bb_Cave39">
        <body>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="zh">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="bold">39</hi>號窟</head>
                <div>
                    <head>概述</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>位置</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>該窟位於南坡<foreign xml:lang="en">B</foreign>區。</item>
                            <item>
                                <foreign xml:lang="en">f</foreign>壁方向：360°。</item>
                        </list>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="bold">39</hi>號窟<foreign xml:lang="en">d</foreign>壁和<hi rend="bold">42</hi>號窟<foreign xml:lang="en">f</foreign>壁相距約13米。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>形制</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>敞口方形窟，雙層窟口，窟室平面為方形，平頂。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>尺寸</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>窟底高於現在的小徑約2.5米。</item>
                            <item>內窟口前部寬度為232釐米；外窟口寬度為280釐米，內外窟口間進深48釐米。</item>
                            <item>石窟進深：227釐米。</item>
                            <item>高度：內部高270釐米，外部高305釐米（門楣區已脫落）。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>保存狀況</head>
                        <p>該窟已完全鑿空，但壁面尚未打磨，也沒有刊刻任何文字。</p>
                        <figure rend="page" n="figure" xml:id="cave_39_DSC_0100.JPG">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">
                                <hi rend="bold">39</hi>號窟所在位置高於小徑約2.5米；2010年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Location of cave <hi rend="bold">39</hi>, ca. 2.5 m above the walkway; 
                                photograph taken in 2010</head>
                            <graphic url="cave_39_DSC_0100.JPG"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="en">
                <head type="cave">Cave <hi rend="bold">39</hi>
                </head>
                <div>
                    <head>Description</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>Location</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Southern slope, section B </item>
                            <item>Direction: wall f 360˚</item>
                        </list>
                        <p>The distance from wall d of cave <hi rend="bold">39</hi>, to wall f of cave <hi rend="bold">42</hi> is ca. 13 meters.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Shape</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Box shape, open at front; double entrance, square ground plan, flat ceiling.</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Measurements</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Height above present walkway: ca. 2.5 meters</item>
                            <item>Width of opening at front 232 cm; outer opening: 280 cm, depth 48 cm</item>
                            <item>Depth: 227 cm</item>
                            <item>Height: inside 270 cm; outside 305 cm (lintel area fallen off)</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>State of preservation</head>
                        <p>The cave is completely hollowed out, but the walls remain unpolished, and no inscriptions were carved. </p>
                        <figure rend="page" n="figure" xml:id="cave_39_DSC_1464.JPG">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">
                                <hi rend="bold">39</hi>號窟，其內壁未及打磨和刊刻文字；2010年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Cave <hi rend="bold">39</hi>, with walls ready for polishing and carving; 
                                photograph taken in 2010</head>
                            <graphic url="cave_39_DSC_1464.JPG"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
